<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verificador de autenticidade - <%= contract.title %></title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://i.ibb.co/60sW9k75/logo.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }
        .layout {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
            gap: 32px;
            align-items: start;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        .panel-left {
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }
        .panel-left h2 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #FFC700;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .panel-left ul {
            list-style: none;
        }
        .panel-left li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .panel-left li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .panel-left li i { color: #22c55e; }
        .panel-right {
            background: #fff;
            color: #1e293b;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .panel-right h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .update-time {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
            color: #16a34a;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .status-badge i { font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .info-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-block label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .info-block .value {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .hash-value {
            font-family: 'Consolas', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #334155;
        }
        .download-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .download-btns a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .download-btns a.primary {
            background: #FFC700;
            color: #000;
        }
        .download-btns a.secondary {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #475569;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .download-btns a:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .signatures-section {
            margin-top: 28px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .signatures-section h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .signer-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .signer-card .badges {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .signer-card .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
            color: #16a34a;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .signer-card .name {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .signer-card .date {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .legal {
            margin-top: 24px;
            padding-top: 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #64748b;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="layout">
        <aside class="panel-left">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Verificador de autenticidade</h2>
            <p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.5;">
                Verifique, de maneira rápida e segura, a autenticidade das assinaturas em seus documentos com o ConectaKing.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Valida documentos sem fricções</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Mitiga riscos de falsificação</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Previne fraudes por manipulação</li>
            </ul>
        </aside>
        <main class="panel-right">
            <h1>Verificador de autenticidade</h1>
            <p class="update-time">Última atualização em <%= new Date().toLocaleString('pt-BR', { dateStyle: 'long', timeStyle: 'short' }) %></p>

            <div class="status-badge">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                <% if (contract.status === 'completed') { %>
                    Status: Concluído
                <% } else { %>
                    Status: <%= contract.status === 'cancelled' ? 'Cancelado' : 'Em andamento' %>
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="info-block">
                <label>Número</label>
                <div class="value"><%= contract.id %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-block">
                <label>Documento</label>
                <div class="value"><%= (contract.title || 'Contrato').substring(0, 120) %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-block">
                <label>Data da criação</label>
                <div class="value"><%= new Date(contract.created_at).toLocaleString('pt-BR') %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-block">
                <label>Hash do documento original (SHA256)</label>
                <div class="hash-value"><%= contract.original_pdf_hash || 'N/A' %></div>
            </div>
            <% if (contract.final_pdf_hash) { %>
            <div class="info-block">
                <label>Hash do documento assinado (SHA256)</label>
                <div class="hash-value"><%= contract.final_pdf_hash %></div>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="download-btns">
                <% if (contract.status === 'completed' && contract.final_pdf_url) { %>
                    <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/contract/download/<%= contract.id %>" class="primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                        <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download do documento assinado
                    </a>
                <% } %>
                <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/api/contracts/<%= contract.id %>/pdf" class="secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    <i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> Ver PDF original
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="signatures-section">
                <h3>Assinaturas: <%= signatures.length %> de <%= signers.length %> assinaturas</h3>
                <div class="badge" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15); color: #16a34a; padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i> Autenticação reconhecida pelo ConectaKing
                </div>
                <% signatures.forEach(function (sig) { %>
                <div class="signer-card">
                    <div class="badges">
                        <span class="badge"><i class="fas fa-pen-fancy"></i> Assinado</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="name"><%= (sig.signer_name || 'Signatário').trim() || 'Signatário' %></div>
                    <div class="date">Data e hora: <%= new Date(sig.signed_at).toLocaleString('pt-BR') %></div>
                </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>

            <div class="legal">
                Conforme MP 2.200-2/2001 e Lei 14.063/2020. As assinaturas eletrônicas têm eficácia jurídica nos termos da legislação brasileira. Este documento foi gerado automaticamente pelo sistema ConectaKing.
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
